Project Bureau — ATF1504AS Block C Macrocells

Project Bureau aims at documenting the bitstream format of Microchip ATF15xx CPLDs. This is a work in progress. See more in the repository.

Macrocell Configuration Bitmap

Logic block C uses 379 (known) fuses within range 30720..32640 for macrocells MC33, MC34, MC35, MC36, MC37, MC38, MC39, MC40, MC41, MC42, MC43, MC44, MC45, MC46, MC47, MC48.
